      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those looking for a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some scratches on the exterior and minor wear on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, though it may soon require some routine service for wear-and-tear items like tires or brake pads. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that performs its duties well without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
