      "description": "Hey! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total beauty. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always kept in the garage, hand-washed every weekend, and it still smells like it just left the showroom! It\u2019s in truly flawless condition inside and out, and it drives like a dream. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move fast. You\u2019ve seriously got to see this one in person to believe how clean it is\u2014drop me a message and come take a look!",
