    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically superlative; the high-pressure Double-VANOS system has been recalibrated, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance to ensure internal longevity. The chassis is structurally sound with a professionally reinforced rear subframe. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-differential, providing linear torque delivery and exceptional turn-in. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers. Finished in pristine Alpine White over Nappa leather, this is a turn-key example for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
