      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and firm, still carrying that distinct 'new car' aroma and showing no signs of wear on the bolsters. Every electronic feature, from the advanced navigation system to the premium surround-sound audio, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians; a comprehensive binder of service records is included. The alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash, and are wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner.",
